title: XOOS
message: >-
  If you use this software, please cite it using the
  metadata from this file.
type: software
abstract: >-
  A collection of secondary analysis tools to build pipelines
  for analyzing SBX sequencing data. For Research Use Only.
  Not for use in diagnostic procedures.
